{"html":"<section id=\"epigraph\">\n\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>The blacker the berry</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>The sweeter the juice⁠ ⁠…</span>\n\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t<cite>Negro folk saying</cite>\n\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>My color shrouds me in.⁠ ⁠…</span>\n\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t<cite>Countee Cullen</cite>\n\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t</section>"}